7 PART VI
8 SECTION 10. Salary increases and cost adjustments provided
9 in this Act for any officer or employee whose compensation is
10 paid, in whole or in part, from federal, special, or other funds
11 shall be paid wholly or proportionately, as the case may be,
12 from the respective funds.
13 SECTION 11. The fiscal year 2025-2026 appropriations or
14 authorizations under this Act shall not lapse until the end of
15 the fiscal biennium 2025-2027; provided that funds appropriated
16 or authorized by this Act that are not expended or encumbered by
17 June 30, 2027, shall lapse as of that date.
